Introduction

BuildVerse DreamVerse ke andar ek Mega Mini Game hai.

Iska main concept sirf city banana nahi hai.

Iska asli goal hai:

«"Build a City, Then Live Inside It."»

Player sirf buildings place nahi karega.

Player apni banayi hui city ke andar:

- Walk karega.
- Car drive karega.
- Buildings ke andar enter karega.
- NPCs ke saath interact karega.
- Apni city ko ek living world ki tarah experience karega.

Ye BuildVerse ko normal city-building games se alag banata hai.

---

Mega Mini Game Structure

DreamVerse ke andar bahut saare Mega Mini Games honge.

BuildVerse unme se pehla Mega Mini Game hai.

Concept:

DreamVerse
│
├── BuildVerse
├── FashionVerse
├── FoodVerse
├── DriveVerse
├── SportsVerse
├── PartyVerse
├── AdventureVerse
├── PetVerse
├── CreativeVerse
└── FamilyVerse

Har Mega Mini Game ke andar us category ke multiple game modes honge.

