Residential System

Player decide karega:

- Residential Area
- Commercial Area
- Government Area
- Industrial Area
- Park Area

Lekin BuildVerse me sirf zoning nahi hogi.

Player chahe to manually bhi buildings place kar sakega.

Isse freedom aur creativity dono milengi.

