Maintenance Department

Har utility aur government service ki apni maintenance team hogi.

Departments:

- Water Department
- Electricity Department
- Gas Department
- Police Department
- Fire Department
- Hospital Department
- Garbage Department
- Internet Department
- Railway Department
- Airport Department
- Park Department

Har department me maximum 10 workers rakhe ja sakte hain.

Player decide karega:

- Kisko hire karna hai.
- Kisko fire karna hai.
- Kisko promotion dena hai.

Har NPC worker ka profile hoga.

Example:

- Age
- Experience
- Education
- Skills
- Behaviour
- Salary
- Performance
- Attendance

---

Job Application Center

Har department ka apna Office hoga.

NPC khud jobs ke liye apply karenge.

Player unka profile dekhkar select karega.

Agar city badi hogi to skilled workers ki demand bhi badhegi.

---

Employee Salary System

Har employee ko regular salary deni hogi.

Agar salary bahut din tak nahi mili:

- Motivation kam hoga.
- Complaint karega.
- Job chhod sakta hai.
- Dusri city me shift bhi ho sakta hai.

Agar worker kaamchor hua:

Player usko:

- Warning de sakta hai.
- Training de sakta hai.
- Fire kar sakta hai.

---

Tax System

Tax system simple aur fun rahega.

Player sliders ke through tax decide karega.

Examples:

- House Tax
- Shop Tax
- Factory Tax
- Vehicle Tax
- Event Tax

Sab percentage me honge.

Example:

House Tax = 5%

Shop Tax = 8%

Factory Tax = 10%

Agar tax bahut zyada hua:

Citizens complaint karenge.

Happiness kam hogi.

Agar tax bahut kam hua:

Citizens khush rahenge.

Lekin Government ki income kam ho jayegi.

Player ko balance maintain karna padega.

