Citizen Complaint System

NPC sirf Report Card me numbers nahi honge.

Wo directly Mayor ko messages bhejenge.

Examples:

💧 Water Problem

"3 din se pani nahi aa raha."

⚡ Electricity

"Bijli baar-baar ja rahi hai."

🏫 School

"School bahut chhota pad gaya."

